OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPeriod products for NHS    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fstaff 'a basic necessity'  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A leading Scottish ICU consultant has  
OL,6, told the BBC of the dread female staff 
OL,7, can feel knowing that they could be    
OL,8, about to bleed through their scrubs but
OL,9, have no access to pads or tampons.     
OL,11,FDr Rosie Baruah backed the BMA's call  
OL,12,Ffor period products to be provided in  
OL,13,Fall NHS staff toilets.                 
OL,15,FShe said the products should be viewed 
OL,16,Fas a basic necessity not a luxury.     
OL,18,FThe British Medical Association said it
OL,19,Fwas a dignity in work issue and called 
OL,20,Ffor all staff to have access.          
